normalised: Khanthi bima, na? Behut nangou, jekha be bochorni Bihar-ni mousumi barhwi bohor jaboiyanikhai. Angni gaonni Ramlal bai gwiyan khetramfwi gabu gabwi gwi jadoong. PM Fasal Bima Yojana ni raimwi khanay, gwi boi dong. Bisuwi ni bisanwi Julai ni barhwi jaboiyanikhai sumai sumai khanay biyanjoi? Kisan Credit Card gaba joi boi? Bosuwi ni bisanwi August ni samfang twi baje'o ICAR ni munsang'o hargwi biyanjoi. Bosuwi ni bisanwi Jonwari ni gathwi baje'o, ek acre o raimwi hazaar anwi ba dong, be to gabu gabwi gwi joi! Jai Kisan!

unnormalised: बे बोसोर बिहारआव दावहागोन मोनसोँ थानायनिफ्रायनो, बेयो गियान खुलुगा।
